default The National Crime Recording Standard
default&#xa0;
default(NCRS) is a standard for recording crime in accordance with the
default law.
default&#xa0;
defaultIt is based on applying legal definitions of crime to victim’s reports. The aim of NCRS is to
default&#xa0;
defaultbe victim focussed and maintain a consistent data set of recorded
default&#xa0;
defaultcrime allegations across all forces. See 
